Package: ggmethylation
Title: Read-Level Methylation Visualisation from Long-Read Sequencing
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Luuk", "Harbers", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "l.j.w.harbers@gmail.com")
Author: Luuk Harbers [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Luuk Harbers <l.j.w.harbers@gmail.com>
Description: Visualise read-level base modification data from long-read
    sequencing (Oxford Nanopore, PacBio). Parses MM/ML tags from modBAM
    files and produces ggplot2 read-level methylation plots with optional
    group summary panels.
